---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Events & Parties — Book the Whole Place Out | Tennis Terminal"
  description="Birthdays, team offsites, league nights and kids' parties on the Brooklyn waterfront. We set up the bays and machines — you bring the crew."
  path="/events"
>
  <section style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,84px) 24px clamp(24px,4vw,40px);text-align:center">
    <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);margin-bottom:16px">Events &amp; parties</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(38px,5.4vw,60px);line-height:1.04;max-width:16ch;margin:0 auto">Book the whole place out</h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:clamp(17px,2.2vw,20px);line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin:20px auto 0;max-width:52ch;text-wrap:pretty">Birthdays, team offsites, league nights, kids' parties — take over the bays for a couple of hours. We set up the machines, you bring the crew. Beginners more than welcome.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- PACKAGES -->
  <section style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(16px,3vw,32px) 24px clamp(40px,6vw,64px)">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:22px;align-items:stretch">
      <div style="background:var(--tt-white);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:18px;padding:32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column">
        <h3 style="font-size:24px">Birthday bash</h3>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:12px;flex:1">Two bays, two hours, all the balls you can hit. Great for kids and grown-ups alike — we'll keep the feed gentle for first-timers.</p>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:28px;color:var(--tt-court-ink);margin-top:20px">From $180</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-ink-300);margin-top:4px">Up to 8 guests</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--tt-court-ink);border-radius:18px;padding:32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(22,59,42,0.18)">
        <span style="align-self:flex-start;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-court-ink);background:var(--tt-marigold);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:999px">Most popular</span>
        <h3 style="font-size:24px;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);margin-top:16px">Team offsite</h3>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);opacity:0.85;margin-top:12px;flex:1">Whole-venue buyout for up to 16. A round-robin, a little coaching, zero pressure — the easiest team hang you'll plan all quarter.</p>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:28px;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);margin-top:20px">From $360</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-marigold);margin-top:4px">All four bays</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--tt-white);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:18px;padding:32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column">
        <h3 style="font-size:24px">League night</h3>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:12px;flex:1">A standing weekly slot for your crew — same bay, same time, locked in for the season. We'll help you run the ladder.</p>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:28px;color:var(--tt-court-ink);margin-top:20px">Let's talk</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-ink-300);margin-top:4px">Recurring rate</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW EVENTS WORK -->
  <section style="background:var(--tt-white);border-top:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade)">
    <div style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,84px) 24px">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:36px"><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);margin-bottom:14px">How it works</div><h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,3.8vw,40px);line-height:1.08">Planning one is easy</h2></div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px">
        <div style="display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:flex-start;background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:14px;padding:22px 24px"><span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);color:var(--tt-play-green);font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px">01</span><div><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:18px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">Tell us the basics</div><p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:4px">Date, headcount, and whether it's tennis, pickleball, or a bit of both.</p></div></div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:flex-start;background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:14px;padding:22px 24px"><span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);color:var(--tt-play-green);font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px">02</span><div><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:18px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">We set the room</div><p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:4px">Bays converted, machines loaded, gear laid out — ready before your first guest arrives.</p></div></div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:flex-start;background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:14px;padding:22px 24px"><span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);color:var(--tt-play-green);font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px">03</span><div><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:18px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">You just show up</div><p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:4px">Bring food and drinks if you like — there's room to gather between games.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,80px) 24px;text-align:center">
    <h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,40px);line-height:1.1">Let's plan your event</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:14px">Tell us what you're dreaming up and we'll sort the rest.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:26px">
      <a href="mailto:events@tennisterminal.com" style="display:inline-block;font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:16px;color:var(--color-primary-on);background:var(--tt-play-green);padding:15px 30px;border-radius:10px">Email the events team</a>
      <a href="/join" style="display:inline-block;font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-court-ink);background:var(--tt-white);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);padding:15px 30px;border-radius:10px">Join the waitlist</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
